channel.title: A model with no collision?
channel.description:
It happened just after I acquired a crowbar. I checked it multiple times, I can go into it just as if I was using noclip. What's even more strange, if I look away from it for a few seconds, it disappears (last picture). [url]https://imgur.com/a/3V9Oa[/url]
Also... is this tie supposed to look like that? [url]https://imageshack.us/a/img269/4315/2012091400001.jpg[/url]
